



CinsayShaunz (SinSAYShawnz) is a sensational little jewelry boutique located in the center of Davis.  They specialize in unique, handcrafted designs of sterling silver, semiprecious Geology stones and natural elements and feature some of  Northern California Northern Californias hottest Local Artists artists.  Their customers describe them as a “treasure in the heart of Davis”.  CinsayShaunz approaches business with the philosophy that by helping one artist, they help Art the community.  We work with local artists of all ages to bring beautiful and original designs to their customers.  Whether old or young, they have something for you: from specialized childrens jewelry to bold beautiful pieces  they have something for everyone

